<i>verb</i>: 흩어지다 [흐터지다], 흩뜨리다 [흗뜨리다], 흩다 [흗따], 흩날리다 [흔날리다], 흐트러뜨리다 [흐트러뜨리다], 헤지다 [헤ː지다], 헤어지다 [헤어지다], 늘어놓다 [느러노타] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>흩어지다 [흐터지다]</dt><br>
<dd>scatter; disperse</dd><br>
<dd>한데 모였던 것이 따로따로 떨어지거나 여러 곳으로 퍼지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For something stuck together to fall apart separately or spread out in all directions.</dd><br>
<dt>흩뜨리다 [흗뜨리다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. scatter; disperse</dd><br>
<dd>흩어지게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make something scatter.</dd><br>
<dd>2. disarrange; put in disorder</dd><br>
<dd>태도, 마음, 옷차림 등을 바르게 하지 못하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To fail to adjust oneself or straighten out one's attitude or mind, etc.</dd><br>
<dt>흩다 [흗따]</dt><br>
<dd>scatter; disperse; separate</dd><br>
<dd>모였던 것을 따로따로 떨어지게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>For something stuck together to fall apart separately.</dd><br>
<dt>흩날리다 [흔날리다]</dt><br>
<dd>flutter; scatter</dd><br>
<dd>흩어져 날리다. 또는 그렇게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To scatter and blow; or to make this happen.</dd><br>
<dt>흐트러뜨리다 [흐트러뜨리다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. scatter; dishevel; rumple</dd><br>
<dd>따로따로 흩어져 이리저리 얽히게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To scatter things and make them entangled in a disorderly manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. make untidy; disarrange; distort</dd><br>
<dd>겉모습, 자세, 태도 등을 단정하지 않게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To lose one's composure in posture or fail to straighten one's conduct, attitude, etc.</dd><br>
<dd>3. confuse; tarnish; unsettle</dd><br>
<dd>정신을 어지럽게 하여 집중하지 못하게 하다.</dd><br>
<dd>To distract someone to keep him/her from concentrating on something.</dd><br>
<dt>헤지다 [헤ː지다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. part; bid farewell; say good-bye</dd><br>
<dd>같이 있던 사람과 떨어지다.</dd><br>
<dd>To part with another one has been with.</dd><br>
<dd>2. break up; split up; divorce</dd><br>
<dd>친하게 지내던 사람과 관계를 끊다.</dd><br>
<dd>To cut off a relationship with someone one is on close terms with.</dd><br>
<dd>3. separate; disperse; scatter</dd><br>
<dd>모여 있던 것들이 따로따로 흩어지거나 떨어지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For something stuck together to fall apart or scatter.</dd><br>
<dd>4. split; crack</dd><br>
<dd>피부가 터져 갈라지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For the skin to be split and cracked.</dd><br>
<dt>헤어지다 [헤어지다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. part; bid farewell; say good-bye</dd><br>
<dd>같이 있던 사람과 떨어지다.</dd><br>
<dd>To part with another one has been with.</dd><br>
<dd>2. break up; split up; divorce</dd><br>
<dd>친하게 지내던 사람과 관계를 끊다.</dd><br>
<dd>To cut off one's relationship with someone one is on close terms with.</dd><br>
<dd>3. separate; disperse; scatter</dd><br>
<dd>모여 있던 것들이 따로따로 흩어지거나 떨어지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For something stuck together to fall apart or scatter.</dd><br>
<dd>4. split; crack</dd><br>
<dd>피부가 터져 갈라지다.</dd><br>
<dd>For the skin to be split and cracked.</dd><br>
<dt>늘어놓다 [느러노타]</dt><br>
<dd>1. arrange; display</dd><br>
<dd>물건 등을 줄지어 벌여 놓다.</dd><br>
<dd>To put things, etc., in a row.</dd><br>
<dd>2. scatter; put in disorder</dd><br>
<dd>여기저기에 어수선하게 두다.</dd><br>
<dd>To put things here and there disorderedly.</dd><br>
<dd>3. attempt various tasks; extend one's business in all directions</dd><br>
<dd>여러 가지 일을 한꺼번에 어수선하게 벌여 놓다.</dd><br>
<dd>To get many things going in a disorderly fashion.</dd><br>
<dd>4. harp on the same string; speak at length</dd><br>
<dd>중요하지 않은 말이나 글 등을 길게 말하거나 쓰다.</dd><br>
<dd>To speak or write something unimportant in a lengthy manner.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>